<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New Job Opportunity</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb, #2575fc);
      color: #333333;
    }

    .email-container {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid #e3e3e3;
    }

    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #5e6ad2, #4f4eff);
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .content h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      color: #4f4eff;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .content p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #555555;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }

    .job-details {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      border: 1px solid #dedede;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      text-align: left;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .job-details p {
      margin: 8px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #444444;
    }

    .job-details p strong {
      color: #333333;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #ffffff;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4f4eff, #6a11cb);
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: bold;
      box-shadow: 0 3px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }

    .button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #f1f1f1;
      padding: 15px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #888888;
    }

    .footer p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>New Job Opportunity!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Take Your Career to the Next Level</h2>
      <p>We are excited to share a job opening that matches your skills and aspirations. Check out the details below and
        don't miss this chance!</p>
      <div class="job-details">
        <p><strong>Job Title:</strong> <%= jobTitle %></p>
        <p><strong>Location:</strong> <%= jobLocation %></p>
        <p><strong>Type:</strong> <%= jobType %></p>
        <p><strong>Salary:</strong> <%= jobSalary %> LPA</p>
      </div>
      <a href="<%= jobLink %>" class="button">View Job Details</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:udaydivyaclinic@gmail.com">udaydivyaclinic@gmail.com</a>.</p>
      <p>You are receiving this email because you subscribed to our job alerts.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
